summary: NAR 03-25-2003        MR.  IN FEB 2003 THE CONSUMER RECEIVED A LETTER IN THE MAIL REGARDING A SPECIAL POLICY FOR CERTAIN SATURN VEHICLES BUILT AFTER MARCH 31, 1995.  THE REPORT ADDRESSED FRONT SEAT BACK SLIPS PARTIALLY REARWARD.  IN JAN 2003 THE CONSUMERS VEHICLE WAS REAR ENDED, THE SEAT BACK RECLINER MECHANISM FAILED AND THE SEAT BACK INSTANTLY COLLAPSED AGAINST THE REAR SEAT. (SATURN 1994)(JB
